      "answer": "D",
      "explanation": "$12:19=\\dfrac{12}{19}$。$\\dfrac{1}{19}:\\dfrac{1}{12}=\\dfrac{1}{19}\\div\\dfrac{1}{12}=\\dfrac{12}{19}$ ✓。其它都不等于 $\\dfrac{12}{19}$。"
